    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/b68dbb83048f79510c8534203aaa8579.poster.avif?t=1750073661\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/b68dbb83048f79510c8534203aaa8579.webm?t=1750073661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/b68dbb83048f79510c8534203aaa8579.mp4?t=1750073661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在《<strong>Hard West 2</strong>》中重返西部的黑暗之心。<br><br>扮演Gin Carter, 化身臭名昭著的亡命之徒。<br><br>在打探消息的过程中，你无意间得知有一辆满载着联邦黄金的“<i>幽灵列车</i>”正朝着你的方向急速飞驰而来。机会来了。<br><br>你迅速组织起了一支强盗队伍：除了寻常的使枪好手之外，还有一些能够凭借超自然能力让嘈杂酒吧瞬间鸦雀无声的特殊人士。<br><br>伴随着夜幕降临，你的队伍策马奔腾，皎洁的月光之下只能看见几个上下翻腾的身影。在枪林弹雨的回想与牺牲品的尖叫之中，你们将荒凉原野彻底转化为了无法无天的恶行之地。<br><br>但是等到终于登上列车之后，你们才发现“<i>幽灵列车</i>”原来并非徒有其名。为了自身的救赎，你们别无选择，只能在子弹与巫术的陪伴下深入Hard West,从未有人探索过的蛮荒恶土。<br><br>追捕恶魔本尊，夺回你们被他夺走的……灵魂。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点：</h2><strong>好人，恶人与不死人：</strong> 当遥远西部的民间传说与诡异秘教的黑暗知识激荡碰撞，在冷酷无情的险恶之地面对成群结队的恶魔与枪林弹雨。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/31213cc6223bab02ed72d151ab5eb1d0.poster.avif?t=1750073661\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/31213cc6223bab02ed72d151ab5eb1d0.webm?t=1750073661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/31213cc6223bab02ed72d151ab5eb1d0.mp4?t=1750073661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>征服黑暗边疆：</strong> 探索狂野西部的真正边陲，赌上一切拯救自己的灵魂。在冒险途中逐步了解队伍成员的秘密，从白雪皑皑的山峦到真正的拓荒小镇，在这个残酷世界中挣扎求生。做出艰难抉择，面对惊骇可怕的后果。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/6bd374201176fec8e7841ddb2443c4c8.poster.avif?t=1750073661\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/6bd374201176fec8e7841ddb2443c4c8.webm?t=1750073661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/6bd374201176fec8e7841ddb2443c4c8.mp4?t=1750073661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>展现你的Bravado：</strong> 通过持续击杀激活Bravado状态并立刻恢复全部行动点，无论什么妖魔鬼怪，都妄想阻止你们的脚步。以流畅潇洒的动作连续击杀多名敌人，化身真正的传奇枪手。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/7b0bb4050fa3d81c80f1c5135beb456c.poster.avif?t=1750073661\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/7b0bb4050fa3d81c80f1c5135beb456c.webm?t=1750073661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/7b0bb4050fa3d81c80f1c5135beb456c.mp4?t=1750073661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>超能恶棍：</strong> 寻找神秘扑克牌，构筑专属牌组，为队伍成员提供火力凶猛的枪支，炸弹，物件或者是借助烤豆子和威士忌的扎实一餐让所有人重整雄风。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/bc30acb96b3893eb42befce3af9b1e8e.poster.avif?t=1750073661\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/bc30acb96b3893eb42befce3af9b1e8e.webm?t=1750073661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/bc30acb96b3893eb42befce3af9b1e8e.mp4?t=1750073661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>意料之外的领袖：</strong> 不管你想不想要担起这份责任，你都需要好好照顾日益壮大的队伍中的每一位快枪手，传送女巫或者是其他千奇百怪的神秘存在。但是也不要忘记好好聆听队友们的心声，斟酌你给他们下达的命令。正确的选择将能带来更多忠诚点，而最亲近的同伴更是能解锁有用的全新技能，但是如果薄情寡义，那么小心他们随时离你而去。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/50c5434d857fe05c01b1caeeec2b6183.poster.avif?t=1750073661\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/50c5434d857fe05c01b1caeeec2b6183.webm?t=1750073661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/50c5434d857fe05c01b1caeeec2b6183.mp4?t=1750073661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>瞬息万变的枪战：</strong> 在铅弹与巫术能量的指引下，你将需要在动态环境中开展回合制战斗，考验枪法，更考验脑力。彻底释放对于西部的一切狂野幻想，不管是骑马追击还是紧张刺激的列车结案，在挑战中磨练你的策略定夺。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/6e8044fd6729ec154ea0de41847890c3.poster.avif?t=1750073661\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/6e8044fd6729ec154ea0de41847890c3.webm?t=1750073661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1282410/extras/6e8044fd6729ec154ea0de41847890c3.mp4?t=1750073661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
